Install Notes
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------


This torrent contains freeware from the official site of the developper.
Check their TOS for more information.

SKINS: Windows 2000 - XP

1. Place the zip file in your Xfire skins folder. The default path is: 
C:\Program Files\Xfire\skins.
2. Exit and Restart your Xfire. Just logging off and back on will not work when 
adding a new skin.
3. On your Xfire client click Tools, then Skin, a list of your installed 
skins will appear. Select the skin of your choice to load it.
4. Enjoy your new Xfire skin.


SKINS: Windows Vista

1. Place the zip file in your Xfire skins folder. The default path is: 
C:\ProgramData\Xfire\skins\. See Vista Note in the .NFO file if you can not find your 
ProgramData or your Xfire\skins directories.
